{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e58beae85d","title":"在姜黄族英来信上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fc779f77a5","index":0,"year":1955,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"e58beae85d"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"29a84abd7b","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e58beae85d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"姜黄族英，早年从事小学教育工作，是姜济衰的妻子。姜济寰在20世纪20年代和毛泽东相识，曾参加1927年八一南昌起义，后去日本，于1935年病故。1955年4月27日，姜黄族英给毛泽东写信说，她年已六十，生活困难，请求帮她安排一个工作。后被安排为江苏省文史研究馆馆员。"},{"id":"8ccd12635c","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e58beae85d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"徐冰，当时任中共中央统战部副部长。"},{"id":"5a60dccc2d","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e58beae85d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"罗迈，即李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9fe1c9f076","type":"title","text":"在姜黄族英来信”上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e58beae85d"},{"id":"29a84abd7b","type":"paragraph","text":"似可药予帮助，请统战部徐冰同志处理。罗迈知姜济实","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e58beae85d"},{"id":"8ccd12635c","type":"subtitle","text":"为人。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e58beae85d"}],"page":{"id":"4b16082726","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"e58beae85d","start":122,"end":122}}}},"__N_SSG":true}